Build and install spman:

1) Downlad source code:
    https://github.com/MyRequiem/spman/archive/1.0.1.tar.gz
2) tar -xvzf 1.0.1.tar.gz
3) cd spman-1.0.1/slackbuild
4) ./spman.SlackBuild
    The package will be created in the /tmp directory
5) upgradepkg --install-new --reinstall /tmp/spman-1.0.1-noarch-1_myreq.txz
